<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idbddf1dce-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1980—<ref href="/us/pl/96/482">Pub. L. 96–482</ref> substituted “<date date="1979-09-01">September 1, 1979</date>” for “<date date="1976-10-21">October 21, 1976</date>”.</p>
</note>
